        <h3>Equipment Loan</h3>
        <p>
          Grants represent "free money" for funding businesses and non-profits that run by minorities or women, improve the social good, or are engaged in commercializing new technology. Grants represent funds that do not need to be repaid in either cash or equity. The amounts of grants vary between $5,000 and hundreds of thousands of dollars. While no debt is issued from a business bank loan, or equity sold, the organization you receive the grant money from will will likely want to see results from the funding. 
        </p>
        <blockquote>
